	   <tr><td colspan=2>That is NOT an easy one to decide, as there as so many variables Im not sure I could think of all of them.<br><br>At the end of the day, if the races truly are insignificant to you, I'd ask you one question--do you plan on soloing a lot or not?<br><br>If so, then I'd probably take the TRL.&nbsp;&nbsp;If not, I'd probably take the ORG.<br><br>Both make great SKs, just be careful to consider their starting INT when generating the character (ESPECIALLY THE TRL--dump like 15 or all 20 pts into INT).<br><br>Hope that helps<br><br>Lunatic<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
